Engineer - Civil  -
Engineer - Civil
Responsibilities
To coordinate the civil design and engineering activities with the prime objective of ensuring construction activities are built as per design and specification, in line with LCI health and safety procedures and with the objective of meeting project timelines and budgets.  Diploma in civil / structural engineering, or related disciplines ;Undergraduate degree is preferred ;4 – 7 years experience in civil/construction ;Have extensive on-site experience performing construction, road or civil projects ;Have experience in QA/QC training and experience ;Have working experience in civil contractor is preferred ;Basic skills on MS-Word and Excel ;Strong quantitative and numeric skills ;Intermediate skills on Civil/Construction cost planning, cost estimating and analysis ;Able to perform QA/QC system ;Intermediate knowledge of Civil/Construction software/hardware skills ;Proficient in English ;Indonesian citizen.
